==Description==

The [[File:Spreadsheet_AlignVCenter.svg|24px]] '''Spreadsheet AlignVCenter''' tool aligns the contents of selected cells to the center vertically.

==Usage==

# Make sure there is an active [[Spreadsheet_CreateSheet|spreadsheet]].
# Select one or more cells.
# There are several ways to invoke the tool:
#* Press the {{Button|[[File:Spreadsheet_AlignVCenter.svg|16px]] [[Spreadsheet_AlignVCenter|Vertically center-align]]}} button.
#* Select the {{MenuCommand|Spreadsheet → Alignment → [[File:Spreadsheet_AlignVCenter.svg|16px]] Vertically center-align}} option from the menu.


